This progressive program blends endurance, strength, and technique while fostering teamwork, camaraderie, and mental resilience. Participants can challenge themselves or enjoy friendly competition in a supportive environment.

events.title: Women on Weights (WOW)

events.title: Bootcamp
events.description: A 45-minute high intensity class that incorporates plyometric, strength, and interval training. events.title: Swing & West Coast
events.description: What’s the difference between East and West Coast Swing? Come find out! We’ll dance along to jazz, big band, blues, and plenty of contemporary music. Please bring clean smooth-soled shoes for dancing; no experience or dance partner required.
